定處斷。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c865%2c20220426%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPDM,111,簡,865,20220426,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"865","JDATE":"20220426","JTITLE":"竊盜"}